{"review_id": "136562801", "app_id": "1949030", "review_text": "While not being far into the game yet, it does a good job at setting up the stage and telling at atmospheric story in a Lovecraftian environment, but Sherlock Holmes style.\nThere's the mind castle where you can solve the cases, but you need to gather clues first. They can be items, conversation topics or just observations. Then there's two difficulties, one which helps the player a little bit in finding clues, and the other one which doesn't.\n\nI do regularly Let's Play horror (and especially indie horror) games on my YouTube channel. If you want to check out the gameplay, or maybe watch the whole thing, look no further: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BGx6OkjLuhs", "label": 1}
